{"tid":618852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳女咳出腫瘤吞返落肚壓迫食道致嘔 醫生：罕見病例","createTime":"2018-04-06T06:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T16:38:36.000Z","uid":43173,"like":244,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"506cd3e2c5386d70d5b8420417daeaae0ab6df34","tid":618852,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T06:44:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%A5%B3%E5%92%B3%E5%87%BA%E8%85%AB%E7%98%A4%E5%90%9E%E8%BF%94%E8%90%BD%E8%82%9A%E5%A3%93%E8%BF%AB%E9%A3%9F%E9%81%93%E8%87%B4%E5%98%94-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F-%E7%BD%95%E8%A6%8B%E7%97%85%E4%BE%8B-015400550.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E5%259C%25B3%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%2592%25B3%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%2585%25AB%25E7%2598%25A4%25E5%2590%259E%25E8%25BF%2594%25E8%2590%25BD%25E8%2582%259A%25E5%25A3%2593%25E8%25BF%25AB%25E9%25A3%259F%25E9%2581%2593%25E8%2587%25B4%25E5%2598%2594-%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F-%25E7%25BD%2595%25E8%25A6%258B%25E7%2597%2585%25E4%25BE%258B-015400550.html&d=UhcK7O4HZ2YeQOuwrYoL8jQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=0be7f0eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%A5%B3%E5%92%B3%E5%87%BA%E8%85%AB%E7%98%A4%E5%90%9E%E8%BF%94%E8%90%BD%E8%82%9A%E5%A3%93%E8%BF%AB%E9%A3%9F%E9%81%93%E8%87%B4%E5%98%94-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F-%E7%BD%95%E8%A6%8B%E7%97%85%E4%BE%8B-015400550.html</a><br />\n<br />\n深圳一名38歲姓衞女子近日身體不適，一進食即嘔，到北大深圳醫院求醫。醫生查問之下，發現該名女子去年曾大力咳嗽，將食道的腫瘤咳了出來，之後她將腫瘤吞落肚。<br />\n<br />\n衞女表示，近半年已發覺自己吞咽有困難，但因沒有其他症狀，所以不以理會。近日，她開始每次進食都會嘔吐，日漸消瘦，身體狀況愈來愈差，所以到醫院求診。醫生幫衞女檢查食道，發現食道外出現腫瘤，且大到壓迫食道，但基於衛女的胃壁異常厚，且腫瘤旁邊有一個個氣泡的影子，情況與一般外壓性腫瘤不同，令醫生起疑。醫生隨即詢問衞女病歷。<br />\n<br />\n她向醫生透露，去年有一次喉嚨很不舒服，「<span style=\"color: red;\">我就咳了幾下之後&hellip;&hellip;居然&hellip;&hellip;從喉嚨里咳出了一條手指般大小的長條狀物體，又有點像舌頭，當時把我自己嚇壞了，我想把它拉出來，但是拉不動，心里特別害怕，又不知道怎麼辦，我就&hellip;&hellip;趕緊把它又塞回去了。</span>」醫生得悉大為驚訝。<br />\n<br />\n之後醫生為衛女進行手術，把腫瘤切除。主診醫生謝遠財表示，衛女的情況十分罕見，這宗病例是醫院首次遇到。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdaa5f0a7819794e32cbc4632dc13ea84e7af346","tid":618852,"uid":140737,"like":397,"dislike":1,"score":396,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T06:48:37.000Z","msg":"進化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自動去除身體壞組織"},{"pid":"1dcffbe33f3f4cdc190a42fd3de6d8a2b5d486d7","tid":618852,"uid":62532,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T06:49:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜撚野事"},{"pid":"134513d5c8e89913406ceca0d801b8f6dd681a75","tid":618852,"uid":172915,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T06:50:58.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"9c37bd074314757e127ae919949e4d4e17674768","tid":618852,"uid":59898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T06:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5475c8df0c652c35f85a10117bae0962154a413","tid":618852,"uid":40588,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"quote":{"pid":"bdaa5f0a7819794e32cbc4632dc13ea84e7af346","tid":618852,"uid":140737,"like":397,"dislike":1,"score":396,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T06:48:37.000Z","msg":"進化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji